---
title: Thai Beef and Glass Noodles with Carrot Ribbons and Sriracha Dressing
description: Who needs noodles when you could have coodles?! They’re even more fun to make than name; all you’ll need is a vegetable peeler to create perfect noodle ribbons! Tossed with spicy Sriracha dressing, it's a great combination with fun-to-slurp glass noodles.
